    </exercise><exercise id="fs-id2705174" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2705176">    <para id="import-auto-id1168465430004">Hydrogen molecules (molecular mass is equal to 2.016 g/mol) have an average velocity <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>v</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>rms</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow></m:math> equal to 193 m/s. What is the temperature?</para>
